Subject: Re: [VB] re:oil filler prob

The internal pipe wrench for this application is the
1" one.  Be careful not insert it too far into the oil
filler, or you will damage the generator (alternator)
pedestal, and have to wipe out bits of aluminum from
the oil fill hole.

JP

